s="r-bey2uz"><div data-rid="0458188d-eac2-4adc-8603-ba4f76799404" class="r-1ipme0a"><div data-rid="0147ed60-55bd-4474-b48b-2460ca522d01" class="r-vn4vpv"><div data-rid="b833d91f-772b-4b4d-9553-f429322943a8" class="r-1ycu37g"><div data-rid="5502a64f-de1a-4346-8114-292cb39b543f" class="r-w1bum8"><div data-rid="ea183cc7-19ec-4060-8dd3-2deb2750cf66" class="r-bm5pfj alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><h2><strong>5 Reasons Why Sunburst SPF will Keep You From Damaged Skin & Pre-Mature Aging</strong></h2></span></div><div data-rid="e95faf31-1256-4079-b558-da79aa6034e2" class="r-1kp325j alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><h2>There’s a reason Sunburst is <em>The</em> SPF Everyone’s Obsessed With:</h2><p><br></p><p>Aging is inevitable, but the #1 way to slow it down is to wear the right SPF daily. Finding an SPF that works <em>with</em> your skin—not against it—can feel impossible.</p><p><br></p><p>Sunscreens are often comedogenic and clog your pores, causing breakouts. They can feel greasy and heavy on the skin. And worst of all, they can leave you looking ghostly and pale with a white cast.</p><p><br></p><p>Sunburst is different: It delivers serious results without compromise. Whether you're breakout-prone, melasma-prone, or SPF-picky, this one checks all the boxes.</p><p><br></p><p>Made with patented KLEAIR™ Zinc Oxide: 2.45 times more effective at free radical protection than standard zinc oxide. Sunburst is dermatologist tested and approved to protect your skin and combat pre-mature aging.</p><p><br></p><p>Here are five reasons why Sunburst deserves a spot on your shelf:</p></span></div><picture data-rid="d91c851b-652a-45b1-8bb3-aed80bea95ed" class="r-1uidjba"><source srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0003/4580/0755/files/s2780377-av-02_be27cf7b-e093-4ce4-9ce6-1f283ff1d4bb.png?v=1749671382&amp;width=820" media="(max-width: 640px)"/><source srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0003/4580/0755/files/s2780377-av-02_be27cf7b-e093-4ce4-9ce6-1f283ff1d4bb.png?v=1749671382&amp;width=1024" media="(min-width: 641px) and (max-width: 1024px)"/><source srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0003/4580/0755/files/s2780377-av-02_be27cf7b-e093-4ce4-9ce6-1f283ff1d4bb.png?v=1749671382&amp;width=1800" media="(min-width: 1025px) and (max-width: 2400px)"/><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0003/4580/0755/files/s2780377-av-02_be27cf7b-e093-4ce4-9ce6-1f283ff1d4bb.png?v=1749671382" class="r-18hofqn" loading="eager"/></picture></div></div><div data-rid="1c07218c-1c22-4a24-84ad-fcfbd1ecfdcb" class="r-grgxu2"><div data-rid="2b890947-c0db-4abf-a400-344633b36a40" class="r-1ryd0rf"><div data-rid="71b10d31-ddf6-4903-8362-16ae9dcff070" class="r-1unhjcs alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>1.Shield Your Skin from Premature Aging</p></span></div><div data-rid="dbcaf54f-4976-4377-9fb6-085f771bd252" class="r-8lpqfu alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Nothing ages skin faster than UV exposure, which breaks down collagen and leads to fine lines, wrinkles, and sagging over time. Sunburst offers broad-spectrum mineral protection (UVA + UVB) with 12% non‑nano zinc oxide—acting as a physical barrier that blocks the full spectrum of harmful rays before they damage your skin<a href="https://www.blume.com/products/sunburst-mineral-spf-50?srsltid=AfmBOorM7_ZsPKvXdU3Sav7T_9OgSqiwn0FMeoH0PWSA2JXXTwodmOg_&utm_source=chatgpt.com"> </a>Additionally, antioxidants like rosemary extract and vitamin E (tocopherol) neutralize free radicals, preventing radical-induced collagen degradation and supporting long‑term skin resilience. It’s not just sunscreen—it’s an anti‑aging essential packed into your daily routine.</p><p><br></p></span></div></div><picture data-rid="a1c6d741-279f-4a00-af02-0adff13852f6" class="r-vpovlt"><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/d3ed28a8-f6a7-48c8-990f-a1ab9bf9d7ad/5c763fd6-59d1-4ead-a619-9d4bd637d026?width=820" media="(max-width: 640px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/d3ed28a8-f6a7-48c8-990f-a1ab9bf9d7ad/5c763fd6-59d1-4ead-a619-9d4bd637d026?width=1024" media="(min-width: 641px) and (max-width: 1024px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/d3ed28a8-f6a7-48c8-990f-a1ab9bf9d7ad/5c763fd6-59d1-4ead-a619-9d4bd637d026?width=1800" media="(min-width: 1025px) and (max-width: 2400px)"/><img src="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/d3ed28a8-f6a7-48c8-990f-a1ab9bf9d7ad/5c763fd6-59d1-4ead-a619-9d4bd637d026" class="r-sikbc8" loading="lazy"/></picture></div><div data-rid="d78bd652-8e34-43a9-87e5-7163105dbe27" class="r-27zd75"><div data-rid="9cc769fc-1a66-41f4-a333-f6caa96cedf1" class="r-2kjge3"><div data-rid="e2a02189-510c-4048-8f22-6fceb5f9cbe8" class="r-65x0l7 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>2. No White Cast—Just Glow</p></span></div><div data-rid="4700ff65-4795-45b3-8ce5-5f5adde30ee4" class="r-r8bor1 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><h4>The #1 concern people have with mineral SPFs? White cast. Sunburst was formulated to fully blend into all skin tones—from fair to deep—without leaving a chalky residue. Instead, it leaves behind a soft, radiant finish that looks like your skin, only glowier.</h4><p><br></p><p>Say goodbye to dull, lifeless skin! Enriched with Niacinamide, it also helps brighten your complexion, fade dark spots, and even out skin tone, all while providing broad-spectrum sun protection. With regular use, you’ll enjoy a radiant, glowing complexion that stays protected from harmful UV rays.</p></span></div></div><picture data-rid="54c4d6ab-f298-4650-889a-b1dda2decd8b" class="r-1nuv2e1"><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/d3ed28a8-f6a7-48c8-990f-a1ab9bf9d7ad/93a10f15-8a05-44f5-9285-90921660f663?width=820" media="(max-width: 640px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/d3ed28a8-f6a7-48c8-990f-a1ab9bf9d7ad/93a10f15-8a05-44f5-9285-90921660f663?width=1024" media="(min-width: 641px) and (max-width: 1024px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/d3ed28a8-f6a7-48c8-990f-a1ab9bf9d7ad/93a10f15-8a05-44f5-9285-90921660f663?width=1800" media="(min-width: 1025px) and (max-width: 2400px)"/><img src="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/d3ed28a8-f6a7-48c8-990f-a1ab9bf9d7ad/93a10f15-8a05-44f5-9285-90921660f663" class="r-1gesh29" loading="lazy"/></picture></div><div data-rid="69144475-bedf-4bc5-9725-39d2de11f28a" class="r-1b8cry7"><div data-rid="12a238fe-130f-4fd3-9e1e-23c52feef243" class="r-6p6mw3"><div data-rid="53645fef-2783-4df3-a956-2ecad871e574" class="r-r11ikk alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>3. Gentle on Skin, Tough on Results: Acne-Safe and Sensitive Skin-Approved</p></span></div><div data-rid="22dccc5c-4044-43fd-8781-88db5feeaa84" class="r-1yx5sab alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><h4>Breakouts? Redness? Irritation? Not here. Sunburst is powered by calming ingredients like Allantoin and Centella Asiatica, and it’s completely free from pore-clogging oils and harsh actives. It won’t clog pores, and it helps protect healing acne from dark marks or post-inflammatory hyperpigmentation (PIH).</h4><p><br></p><p>If you have sensitive skin, you know the struggle of finding sunscreens that work without irritation. Sunburst is infused with Centella Asiatica and Rosemary Extract, which provide calming and anti-inflammatory benefits while delivering powerful sun protection. It’s gentle enough for all skin types but tough enough to guard against sun damage and environmental stressors.</p></span></div></div><picture data-rid="139f1924-fa89-446e-84b6-c2451930cec0" class="r-i694n3"><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/d3ed28a8-f6a7-48c8-990f-a1ab9bf9d7ad/f51c4289-0f3f-47ca-9b8a-80cac5a2b2d1?width=820" media="(max-width: 640px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/d3ed28a8-f6a7-48c8-990f-a1ab9bf9d7ad/f51c4289-0f3f-47ca-9b8a-80cac5a2b2d1?width=1024" media="(min-width: 641px) and (max-width: 1024px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/d3ed28a8-f6a7-48c8-990f-a1ab9bf9d7ad/f51c4289-0f3f-47ca-9b8a-80cac5a2b2d1?width=1800" media="(min-width: 1025px) and (max-width: 2400px)"/><img src="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/d3ed28a8-f6a7-48c8-990f-a1ab9bf9d7ad/f51c4289-0f3f-47ca-9b8a-80cac5a2b2d1" class="r-ctu8yc" loading="lazy"/></picture></div><div data-rid="c84d486a-b278-48c7-b83a-7d5c5d80d78a" class="r-1wcr8y8"><div data-rid="ac493261-c574-427e-810b-378dc70166ac" class="r-5u47y7"><div data-rid="dc5abc9e-02c6-48ff-8e51-a2dd65ef2997" class="r-jw3rux alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>4. Sunscreen with Skin Care Benefits</p></span></div><div data-rid="dfc3f19e-ac3d-4a7d-a032-88dce4418d61" class="r-t4x5rs alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Let’s face it, some SPFs can feel heavy, sticky, or greasy. Not Sunburst! This SPF features a lightweight, fast-absorbing formula that hydrates deeply without clogging pores or leaving a residue. It soothes and moisturizes the skin, making it perfect for daily use under makeup or on its own. The result? Soft, smooth, and perfectly protected skin that feels as good as it looks.</p><p><br></p><h4>Sunburst has a breathable, fast-absorbing texture that wears beautifully on all skin types—even under makeup. No pilling, no tackiness, no midday oil-slick. Sunburst has been rigorously tested by dermatologists to ensure it’s safe, effective, and suitable for all skin types.</h4></span></div></div><picture data-rid="0ba62624-c6dc-4828-9a4b-a4c7154bc724" class="r-1w8ttzx"><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/d3ed28a8-f6a7-48c8-990f-a1ab9bf9d7ad/9a5304ad-aeb4-4ed3-b24d-e3b0b704b8ae?width=820" media="(max-width: 640px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/d3ed28a8-f6a7-48c8-990f-a1ab9bf9d7ad/9a5304ad-aeb4-4ed3-b24d-e3b0b704b8ae?width=1024" media="(min-width: 641px) and (max-width: 1024px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/d3ed28a8-f6a7-48c8-990f-a1ab9bf9d7ad/9a5304ad-aeb4-4ed3-b24d-e3b0b704b8ae?width=1800" media="(min-width: 1025px) and (max-width: 2400px)"/><img src="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/d3ed28a8-f6a7-48c8-990f-a1ab9bf9d7ad/9a5304ad-aeb4-4ed3-b24d-e3b0b704b8ae" class="r-1aez5oy" loading="lazy"/></picture></div><div data-rid="ad456288-18a6-4d34-81d0-54b7ee53a704" class="r-1ty0zyw"><div data-rid="1db64263-0730-4f01-ad98-c1ab75e2e740" class="r-b1c1ht"><div data-rid="a7040ccc-c064-42bc-81a3-146820ffebb2" class="r-1m2zpyq alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>With brightening niacinamide and antioxidant-rich rosemary extract, Sunburst helps fade dark spots, even out tone, and boost radiance over time. Sunburst doesn’t just shield your skin from harmful UV rays—it perfects it too! Its multi-functional formula brightens, hydrates, and fades dark spots while providing essential sun protection. By incorporating this SPF into your daily routine, you’re giving your skin the ultimate care it deserves to stay healthy, radiant, and resilient</p></span></div><div data-rid="390440b4-c722-4cd4-8c3a-4de5d89cf759" class="r-c3goyn alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>5. Brightens, Calms, and Defends against Sunspots and Hyperpigmentation</p></span></div></div></div><picture data-rid="b0fb92b0-4606-4465-9134-ce94c5c38e2f" class="r-1pit9wa"><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/d3ed28a8-f6a7-48c8-990f-a1ab9bf9d7ad/84ef6d65-dc4f-4fc9-a406-1357d6a9c391?width=820" media="(max-width: 640px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/d3ed28a8-f6a7-48c8-990f-a1ab9bf9d7ad/84ef6d65-dc4f-4fc9-a406-1357d6a9c391?width=1024" media="(min-width: 641px) and (max-width: 1024px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/d3ed28a8-f6a7-48c8-990f-a1ab9bf9d7ad/84ef6d65-dc4f-4fc9-a406-1357d6a9c391?width=1800" media="(min-width: 1025px) and (max-width: 2400px)"/><img src="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/d3ed28a8-f6a7-48c8-990f-a1ab9bf9d7ad/84ef6d65-dc4f-4fc9-a406-1357d6a9c391" class="r-1gzqn1f" loading="lazy"/></picture><div data-rid="55f1a208-ad3a-49aa-9bd6-3fc510a73182" class="r-4ln3bj alchemy-rte"><span sty